sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Cache

    Browser->>API: POST /auth/login {email, password}
    API->>Auth: validateCredentials(email, password)
    Auth->>DB: SELECT user WHERE email = ?
    DB-->>Auth: user record
    Auth->>Auth: bcrypt.compare(password, hash)
    Auth-->>API: {userId, roles}
    API->>Auth: generateTokens(userId, roles)
    Auth-->>API: {accessToken, refreshToken}
    API->>Cache: SET session:{userId} refreshToken TTL=7d
    Cache-->>API: OK
    API-->>Browser: 200 {accessToken, refreshToken}

    note over Browser,Cache: Token Refresh Flow

    Browser->>API: POST /auth/refresh {refreshToken}
    API->>Cache: GET session:{userId}
    Cache-->>API: storedRefreshToken
    API->>Auth: rotateTokens(userId, refreshToken)
    Auth-->>API: {newAccessToken, newRefreshToken}
    API->>Cache: SET session:{userId} newRefreshToken TTL=7d
    API-->>Browser: 200 {newAccessToken, newRefreshToken}
